<div id="review_3005145825" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3005145825" />
    <a title="Snehlata Agarwala" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/102565864-snehlata-agarwala"><img alt="Snehlata Agarwala" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1568146495p2/102565864.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3005145825?book_show_action=true">Oct 07, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Snehlata Agarwala" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Snehlata Agarwala" href="/user/show/102565864-snehlata-agarwala">Snehlata Agarwala</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span> (Review from the author)


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102565864-snehlata-agarwala?shelf=young-adults">young-adults</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102565864-snehlata-agarwala?shelf=indian-author">indian-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102565864-snehlata-agarwala?shelf=indie-author">indie-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102565864-snehlata-agarwala?shelf=romance">romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102565864-snehlata-agarwala?shelf=soulmate">soulmate</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102565864-snehlata-agarwala?shelf=suspense">suspense</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3005145825" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6578907042169950133">I know I am the author and I am not entitled to review my own book. But still, I will.<br/>I stated this story just as a chapter in a fb group. And then it kept on building in my mind.<br/>As I wrote this, I fell in love with &quot;Rudra&quot; who as his name states is committed and focused. And a girl, Arya, who is sweet, and had been through a lot in her life. <br/><br/>The Bengali culture is something I have been brought up in, so it is more dear to me than my own marwari culture and you will get a glimpse of my love for </span>
  <span id="freeText6578907042169950133" style="display:none">I know I am the author and I am not entitled to review my own book. But still, I will.<br />I stated this story just as a chapter in a fb group. And then it kept on building in my mind.<br />As I wrote this, I fell in love with "Rudra" who as his name states is committed and focused. And a girl, Arya, who is sweet, and had been through a lot in her life. <br /><br />The Bengali culture is something I have been brought up in, so it is more dear to me than my own marwari culture and you will get a glimpse of my love for it in the story.<br /><br />This was my first story, and I hope I was able to do justice to it.<br /><br />And it is a story of eternal love, because love is always selfless and beautiful. And love always finds it's way. &lt;3 <br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="6578907042169950133" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


