<div id="review_3357235961" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3357235961" />
    <a title="Muskan Singhania" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/84830592-muskan-singhania"><img alt="Muskan Singhania" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3357235961?book_show_action=true">May 26, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Muskan Singhania" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Muskan Singhania" href="/user/show/84830592-muskan-singhania">Muskan Singhania</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3357235961" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7301200803504589868">Let me begin with stating a few words about the story. It is a story of two people so much in love that the universe tries to bring them together in spite of all the barriers and hardships they have faced. Rudra and Arya are the two protagonists of the story who have a magnetic bond attracting them towards each other. The story has been woven together with a Bengali backdrop. The smallest of details that represent Bengali culture has been distinctly stated in the book which paints a picture of t</span>
  <span id="freeText7301200803504589868" style="display:none">Let me begin with stating a few words about the story. It is a story of two people so much in love that the universe tries to bring them together in spite of all the barriers and hardships they have faced. Rudra and Arya are the two protagonists of the story who have a magnetic bond attracting them towards each other. The story has been woven together with a Bengali backdrop. The smallest of details that represent Bengali culture has been distinctly stated in the book which paints a picture of the story in front of your eyes. You can imagine the scenes playing before you, which is a huge accomplishment as a writer. <br />The story as a whole is light and heart-warming. I couldn't keep it aside until it was over. It's a must read for all those who yearn for a beautiful love story.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7301200803504589868" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


