<div id="review_3151305989" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3151305989" />
    <a title="Smitha Nagendra Kini" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/108989223-smitha-nagendra-kini"><img alt="Smitha Nagendra Kini" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3151305989?book_show_action=true">Feb 01, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Smitha Nagendra Kini" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Smitha Nagendra Kini" href="/user/show/108989223-smitha-nagendra-kini">Smitha Nagendra Kini</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3151305989" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8397560769760697687">The first day I read, I just picked a random chapter... but it was sooooo enthralling that I had to begin reading it, the proper way, from the first chapter. <br/><br/>The perfect blend of traditions, relations, romance. The Bengali tradition that&apos;s followed by the characters touched my heart. I loved reading the traditional Sindoor Khela during Pujo. The unconventional way of marriage was so romantic.... the sangam... the subtle involvement of fireflies... the turmoils the characters undergo... the plot.</span>
  <span id="freeText8397560769760697687" style="display:none">The first day I read, I just picked a random chapter... but it was sooooo enthralling that I had to begin reading it, the proper way, from the first chapter. <br /><br />The perfect blend of traditions, relations, romance. The Bengali tradition that's followed by the characters touched my heart. I loved reading the traditional Sindoor Khela during Pujo. The unconventional way of marriage was so romantic.... the sangam... the subtle involvement of fireflies... the turmoils the characters undergo... the plot... all in all this is a wonderful read.<br /><br />This has been the most touching novel ever. </span>
  <a data-text-id="8397560769760697687" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
